h%20burnout%3A%20Admit%20that%20you're%20at%20a%20breaking%20point.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcritical-roles-co-founders-talk-10th-anniversary-releases-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECritical%20Role%3C%2Fa%3E's%20chief%20creative%20officer%2C%20Matthew%20Mercer%2C%20had%20been%20spearheading%20his%20eight-member%20crew's%20relentless%20push%20into%20the%20big%20leagues%20of%20nerdworld%20for%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20until%20this%20July%2C%20when%20he%20announced%20that%20he'd%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcritical-role-campaign-four-matt-mercer-brennan-lee-mulligan-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egiving%20up%20control%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20one%20of%20the%20crew's%20biggest%20priorities%2C%20their%20long-running%20%26quot%3BDungeons%20%26amp%3B%20Dragons%26quot%3B%20Twitch%20livestream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20August%20appearance%20on%20the%20podcast%20%26quot%3BCrispy's%20Tavern%3A%20Tales%20and%20Tea%2C%26quot%3B%20Mercer%20said%20he'd%20felt%20the%20threat%20of%20burnout%20and%20thought%20he%20needed%20a%20break.%20He%20said%20he'd%20started%20to%20feel%20a%20%26quot%3Bcontinuous%20need%20to%20produce%20creatively%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20draining%20and%20very%20scary%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20Mercer%20and%20his%20seven%20cofounders%20still%20have%20a%20full%20slate%20of%20projects%20to%20work%20on.%20That%20includes%20an%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdimension-20-plans-comic-us-tour-madison-square-garden-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esold-out%20arena%20tour%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20two%20Amazon-backed%20animated%20series%20on%20Prime%20Video.%20Mercer%20also%20has%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20team's%20game%20publishing%20arm%2C%20Darrington%20Press%2C%20home%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fm