l%20and%20governance-level%20review%26quot%3B%20and%20remove%20any%20content%20violating%20India's%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Davies-Jones%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom's%20Minister%20for%20Victims%20%26amp%3B%20Violence%20Against%20Women%20and%20Girls%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FAlexDaviesJones%2Fstatus%2F2007079230186930621%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimplored%3C%2Fa%3E%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20X's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-says-xai-acquired-x-in-all-stock-deal-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eparent%20company%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20xAI%2C%20to%20do%20something%20about%20the%20AI%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20care%20so%20much%20about%20women%2C%20why%20are%20you%20allowing%20X%20users%20to%20exploit%20them%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BGrok%20can%20undress%20hundreds%20of%20women%20a%20minute%2C%20often%20without%20the%20knowledge%20or%20consent%20of%20the%20person%20in%20the%20image.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavies-Jones%20also%20referenced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fgovernment-crackdown-on-explicit-deepfakes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUK%20proposal%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20make%20the%20creation%20and%20dissemination%20of%20sexually%20explicit%20deepfakes%20a%20chargeable%20offense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20an%20X%20user%20flagging%20screenshots%20they%20said%20showed%20Grok%20creating%20sexualized%20images%20of%20minors%2C%20the%20official%20Grok%20account%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fgrok%2Fstatus%2F2007006470689214749%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresponded%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20that%20company%20had%20%26quot%3Bidentified%20lapses%20in%20safeguards%20and%20are%20urgently%20fixing%20them%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20though%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20Grok's%20response%20was%20reviewed%20by%20xAI%20or%20simply%20AI%20generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26