wo%20things%20your%20mother%20told%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Rando%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20American%20Federation%20for%20Aging%20Research%20and%20director%20of%20the%20Broad%20Stem%20Cell%20Research%20Center%20at%20UCLA%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEat%20a%20good%20diet%20and%20get%20plenty%20of%20exercise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERando%20dedicated%20his%20career%20to%20studying%20how%20tissues%20repair%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20and%20why%20they%20eventually%20lose%20the%20ability%20to%20do%20it%20well.%20What%20he%20learned%20is%20that%20many%20of%20the%20drugs%20tested%20in%20animals%20that%20are%20meant%20to%20extend%20lifespan%20work%20as%20effectively%20as%20a%20balanced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhabits-longevity-researcher-follows-for-healthy-aging-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ediet%20and%20exercise%20do%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20example%20was%20a%202022%20study%20that%20found%20mice%20that%20were%20put%20on%20fasting%20diets%20were%20as%20resilient%20to%20stress%20as%20those%20injected%20with%20ketone%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20many%20drugs%20and%20interventions%20are%20%26quot%3Bjust%20in%20a%20way%20supplementing%20the%20challenges%20that%20humans%20face%20in%20dieting%20and%20exercising.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224585%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20person%20chopping%20a%20tomato%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ed4cc8cc993f9955d018c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERando%20said%20many%20medications%20compensate%20for%20sedentary%20lifestyles%20and%20eating%20ultra-processed%20foods.%3Cp%3ENathalie%20Pellenkoft%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20own%20life%2C%20he%20said%20his%20research%20hasn't%20inspired%20too%20many%20drastic%20lifestyle%20changes%20as%20much%20as%20reinforcing%20healthy%20habits%2C%20like%20cutting%2